### Maven build artifacts
target/
*.class

### IDE files
.idea/
*.iml
*.iws
*.ipr
.eclipse/
.project
.classpath
.settings/

### OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

### Secrets — never commit
.env

### Sealed secret output (contains encrypted real values — safe to commit
### but only after verifying it contains no plaintext. Excluded by default
### so it must be explicitly added: git add -f k8s/config/sealed-secret.yaml)
k8s/config/sealed-secret.yaml

### TLS certificates (generated locally)
docker/nginx/certs/

### Production keystore — replace the committed dev keystore before deploying.
### Generate: keytool -genkeypair -alias sentinelpay -keyalg RSA -keysize 2048
###           -storetype PKCS12 -keystore keystore.p12 -validity 3650
### Then set SSL_KEYSTORE_PASSWORD in sentinelpay-secrets.
### DO NOT commit a production keystore to git.
api-gateway/src/main/resources/keystore-prod.p12
